page.title: 02A Day In My Life
page.content: At about 6:00 to 6:30 I wake up and go out to help my father at work.I usually help him to feed the cows with cake,clean out the horses and feed the cows with hay.At 7:15 I come in to change into my school clothes and have breakfast. At 8:40 I set out for school.School starts at 9:00.We go into assembly for 30 minutes.Then we go into class and work until 10:40.Then we have a 20 minute break.12:00 is our lunch break until 1:15.We finish school at 3:45. At 4:00 I have tea then I help my father until 7:30.Then I change into my trainers and go running for an hour.At 9:00 I go to bed.
